Package jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml

Class Spatial_Img_SBML

java.lang.Object
jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.Spatial_SBML
jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.Spatial_Img_SBML
All Implemented Interfaces:
ij.plugin.PlugIn
public class Spatial_Img_SBML
extends Spatial_SBML
The class Spatial_Img_SBML. This class calls "run Spatial Image SBML plugin" from ImageJ (XitoSBML). This class is an implementation of XitoSBML as an ImageJ plugin. The run(String) method will call jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.xitosbml.MainImgSpatial#run(java.lang.String). Once registered in src/main/resources/plugins.config, the run() method can be called from the ImageJ menu. Date Created: Jun 17, 2015
Author:
Kaito Ii <ii@fun.bio.keio.ac.jp>, Akira Funahashi <funa@bio.keio.ac.jp>
